Description: Bootstraps your own minimal RaspberryPi SD-card image, supporting various dists,arches and suites.
 Bootstraps your own minimal RaspberryPi SD-card image, supporting various dists,arches and suites. The tool will also download, configure, and install the latest RPi firmware, kernel module etc...
